column2: "<%me>, you're really something to have come this far."
"You're really working hard. I'd like to talk, but now is not a good time."
"Not a good time? Are you expecting something to happen?"
"You don't feel it too, Echo? This tingling feeling in the air?"
"When I get this feeling, it's like something bad is going to happen."
"On that day ten years ago, I had this feeling..."
"I was talking to myself. Forget it."
"Anyway, we're in a strange place, with a threatening sense in the air. We should be on our guard."
"Zeno! Whenever you get on that subject, you immediately back off! Would you stop doing that?"
